# Keep `shopify theme dev`/`push` from trying to upload editor/atomic-save
# temp files. These briefly appear next to a file while it is being saved
# (e.g. templates/index.json.tmp.5848.9075ab011437) and Shopify rejects them
# with "Must have a .liquid file extension".
*.tmp
*.tmp.*
*.temp
*.swp
*.swx
*~
*.bak
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
